Please note:

!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
To successfully run the test suite, the example Rails app needs to be running,
accessible at http://localhost:3000 
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

To add a new test class, include it to TestLoader.java.

Logger may be set to DEBUG in log4j.properties for debugging while running tests.

Please commit tests that pass, or if a test fails, it should clearly indicate the reason why it fails.

